data.name: Label2.Text
data.value: To Add a new portfolio, use the "Browse Portfolio Location" button to find the location of symbols for your new portfolio (create the folder if necessary). Add the name of the portfolio in 5 and then click "Add" (1). This will add the portfolio name to the list at 6 and also store the location of that portfolio.

data.name: Label5.Text
data.value: To Change the name or location of a portfolio, click the portfolio name in 6 (so that it appears in 5), make changes to the name in 5 and its location ("Browse Portfolio Location"), and click "Change" (2). Both the name and location will be saved.
